---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
import "../../styles/globals.css";
import { Header } from "../../components/Header";
import InnerPageCTA from "../../components/InnerPageCTA.astro";
import Footer from "../../components/Footer.astro";

const b = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
---

<Layout
  title="parcelLab Partners with Double Good to Support Its Exponential Growth - parcelLab"
  description="parcelLab partners with Double Good, an e-commerce popcorn fundraising platform, to enhance post-purchase communications and support rapid growth."
>
  <Header client:load />
  <main>
    <!-- Article Header -->
    <section class="section-generous">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-[1440px] px-6 md:px-12">
        <div class="mx-auto max-w-[800px]">
          <a href={`${b}/blog/`} class="group mb-8 inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm font-medium text-[var(--ink-muted)] transition-colors hover:text-[#3D3AD3]">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="transition-transform group-hover:-translate-x-0.5"><path d="M19 12H5"/><path d="m12 19-7-7 7-7"/></svg>
            Back to blog
          </a>
          <span class="mb-4 inline-block rounded-full bg-[#3D3AD3]/10 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-semibold text-[#3D3AD3]">Company News</span>
          <h1 class="text-display text-[var(--ink)]">parcelLab Partners with Double Good to Support Its Exponential Growth</h1>
          <div class="mt-6 flex items-center gap-4 text-sm text-[var(--ink-muted)]">
            <span>By <strong class="font-medium text-[var(--ink-secondary)]">parcelLab Team</strong></span>
            <span class="h-1 w-1 rounded-full bg-[var(--ink-muted)]"></span>
            <time datetime="2022-06-18">June 18, 2022</time>
            <span class="h-1 w-1 rounded-full bg-[var(--ink-muted)]"></span>
            <span>3 min read</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Article Body -->
    <section class="pb-16 md:pb-24">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-[800px] px-6 md:px-12">
        <p class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)] leading-relaxed text-lg">
          parcelLab has announced a partnership with Double Good, an organization revolutionizing product-based online fundraising. The company distributes 50% of revenues to supported organizations and has raised over $200 million for US nonprofits through its e-commerce popcorn platform.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-heading text-[var(--ink)] mt-12 mb-4">The Challenge</h2>
        <p class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)] leading-relaxed">
          Double Good faced significant post-purchase communication obstacles as it scaled rapidly.
        </p>

        <div class="my-10 rounded-2xl bg-[var(--surface-sunken)] p-8">
          <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.1em] text-[var(--ink-muted)]">The Problem</p>
          <p class="mt-2 text-lg font-medium text-[var(--ink)]">"We were limited when we could send delivery surveys to customers. We didn't know when orders arrived at doorsteps."</p>
          <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-[var(--ink-muted)]">-- Anton German, CTO, Double Good</p>
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-heading text-[var(--ink)] mt-12 mb-4">How parcelLab Supports Double Good</h2>
        <p class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)] leading-relaxed">
          The integration leverages parcelLab's API and data infrastructure for production, shipping, and delivery communications. The partnership enables more control between email, text, receipt pages, and pre-checkout, ensuring consistency and personalized messaging at optimal moments.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-heading text-[var(--ink)] mt-12 mb-4">Scalability for Growth</h2>
        <p class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)] leading-relaxed">
          parcelLab's platform supports long-term growth as Double Good expands operations and welcomes additional fundraisers.
        </p>

        <div class="mt-6 space-y-6">
          <div class="rounded-xl border border-[var(--line)] bg-[var(--surface-raised)] p-6">
            <p class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)] leading-relaxed">
              <strong class="text-[var(--ink)]">Tim Heitmann, Double Good founder/CEO:</strong> "The integration bolsters the experience we give shoppers, enabling us to take on more fundraisers than ever before."
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="rounded-xl border border-[var(--line)] bg-[var(--surface-raised)] p-6">
            <p class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)] leading-relaxed">
              <strong class="text-[var(--ink)]">Tobias Buxhoidt, parcelLab CEO:</strong> "Our customizable approach allows customers like Double Good to implement tools rapidly and scale operational support quickly."
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="my-12 border-t border-[var(--line)]"></div>

        <p class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)] leading-relaxed">
          The partnership demonstrates how parcelLab's flexible platform can support organizations of all types -- from traditional retailers to mission-driven e-commerce businesses -- in delivering exceptional post-purchase experiences at scale.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <InnerPageCTA />
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout>
